{"tid":460342,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇N賓同巴斯杜斯離開禾堡有神射手","createTime":"2017-11-06T14:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T19:06:51.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8e35489c7982e7cf9f3fb43c7aa8a8ea8f1c2ae3","tid":460342,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"N賓=聯賽冠軍+神射<br />\n巴斯=葡超神射 爭d贏歐洲金靴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n禾堡呢兩季要護級 肥鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8e799d79f2db4e04f64c077ac4f14746cbe61f","tid":460342,"uid":80736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>N賓=聯賽冠軍+神射<br />\n巴斯=葡超神射 爭d贏歐洲金靴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n禾堡呢兩季要護級 肥鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真連登入面有一班係社會上處於最下游嘅人<br />\n先天條件唔好，後天條件就更加差<br />\n所以對社會上任何事都懷有怨恨<br />\n個個入嚟圍爐，將本身已經扭曲嘅思想變得更扭曲<br />\n人哋話邊個係雞就跟住講，實質一個交心嘅女性frd都無就以為自己睇透世事<br />\n好心啦，呢啲人把口講得咁硬，如果眼前有閪咪又爭住狗衝，地下有金仆過去執<br />\n本質上係同90年代前嘅窮鬼支那人無分別<br />\n大家都係同品同種<br />\n你最好期望呢班窮毒L連登仔唔會他朝有一日發達<br />\n否則往後俾佢哋做到暴發户，就會進化成21世紀大陸蝗、或者而家香港堆old seafood咁乞人憎<br />\n歷史在重覆又重覆<br />\n大家都不自覺跌入呢個螺旋入面<br />\n無。得。救"},{"pid":"4efeed56f375c947db300bf74f4578ef7a259fe8","tid":460342,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>N賓=聯賽冠軍+神射<br />\n巴斯=葡超神射 爭d贏歐洲金靴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/goo